alcatelIND1NETSECMIB.description: This module describes an authoritative enterprise-specific Simple Network Management Protocol (SNMP) Management Information Base (MIB): For the Birds Of Prey Product Line Configuration and monitoring of the EtherBreaker feature. alcatelIND1NETSECMIBNotifications.name: alcatelIND1NETSECMIBNotifications
alcatelIND1NETSECMIBNotifications.description: Branch For NETSEC MIB Subsystem Notifications.

AlaAnomalyType.name: AlaAnomalyType
AlaAnomalyType.description: Types of anomalies being configured or monitored

alaNetSecPortRangeGroupTable.name: alaNetSecPortRangeGroupTable
alaNetSecPortRangeGroupTable.description: Table for collecting port-range and monitoring-group associations. A port belongs to at most one monitoring-group.

alaNetSecPortRangeGroupEntry.name: alaNetSecPortRangeGroupEntry
alaNetSecPortRangeGroupEntry.description: Each entry is identified by a unique port-range.

alaNetSecPortRangeGroupStartIfId.name: alaNetSecPortRangeGroupStartIfId
alaNetSecPortRangeGroupStartIfId.description: Starting interface index of a port-range

alaNetSecPortRangeGroupEndIfId.name: alaNetSecPortRangeGroupEndIfId
alaNetSecPortRangeGroupEndIfId.description: Ending interface index of a port-range

alaNetSecPortRangeGroupName.name: alaNetSecPortRangeGroupName
alaNetSecPortRangeGroupName.description: Name of monitoring-group with which this port-range is associated.

alaNetSecPortRangeGroupRowStatus.name: alaNetSecPortRangeGroupRowStatus
alaNetSecPortRangeGroupRowStatus.description: identifies state of this entry. CREATEANDGO will only work, if the name of alaNetSecPortRangeGroupName is part of the create request

alaNetSecMonitoringGroupTable.name: alaNetSecMonitoringGroupTable
alaNetSecMonitoringGroupTable.description: Table for collecting monitoring-groups' anomaly configurations

alaNetSecMonitoringGroupEntry.name: alaNetSecMonitoringGroupEntry
alaNetSecMonitoringGroupEntry.description: Each entry identifies configuration of a monitoring-group's anomaly-type's parameter

alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyLog.name: alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyLog
alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyLog.description: State of logging upon detecting anomaly.

alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyTrap.name: alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyTrap
alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyTrap.description: State of sending traps upon detecting anomaly.

alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyQuarantin.name: alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyQuarantine
alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyQuarantin.description: State of Quarantining anomalous port upon detecting anomaly.

alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyCount.name: alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyCount
alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyCount.description: Count of packets that must be seen during monitoring period to initiate anomaly detection check. Default value varies as below with anomaly: Anomaly Count ------- ----- ARP address scan 50 ARP flood 90 ARP poisoning 6 ARP Failure 6 ICMP address scan 30 ICMP Flood 90 ICMP Unreachable 20 TCP port Scan 20 TCP address scan 30 SYN flood 90 SYN Failure 10 SYN-ACK Scan 2 FIN Scan 6 FIN-ACK Diff 5 RST Count 50

alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalySensitivi.name: alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalySensitivity
alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalySensitivi.description: Sensitivity of Anomaly Check to deviation from expected behavior.

alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyPeriod.name: alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyPeriod
alaNetSecMonitoringGroupAnomalyPeriod.description: Time in seconds to monitor packets before checking for anomaly.

alaNetSecMonitoringGroupRowStatus.name: alaNetSecMonitoringGroupRowStatus
alaNetSecMonitoringGroupRowStatus.description: CREATEANDGO will only work if, besides RowStatus, at least one of State, Log, Trap, Quarantine, Count, Sensitivity or Period is part of the request.

alaNetSecPortStatsTable.name: alaNetSecPortStatsTable
alaNetSecPortStatsTable.description: Table for reporting port specific statistics

alaNetSecPortStatsEntry.name: alaNetSecPortStatsEntry
alaNetSecPortStatsEntry.description: Stats are collected on a <port,packet-type,packet-direction,total/last> basis

alaNetSecPortStatsLastIngress.name: alaNetSecPortStatsLastIngress
alaNetSecPortStatsLastIngress.description: Count of Indexed Ingress packets observed during last 5 seconds

alaNetSecPortStatsLastEgress.name: alaNetSecPortStatsLastEgress
alaNetSecPortStatsLastEgress.description: Count of Indexed Egress packets observed during last 5 seconds

alaNetSecPortStatsTotalIngress.name: alaNetSecPortStatsTotalIngress
alaNetSecPortStatsTotalIngress.description: Count of Indexed Ingress packets observed since monitoring was enabled, Counter will loop back from zero upon reaching the maximum

alaNetSecPortStatsTotalEgress.name: alaNetSecPortStatsTotalEgress
alaNetSecPortStatsTotalEgress.description: Count of Indexed Egress packets observed since monitoring was enabled. Counter will loop back from zero upon reaching the maximum

alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsEntry.name: alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsEntry
alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsEntry.description: Stats are collected on a <port,anomaly-type,packet-type,packet-direction,current/last> basis

alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsCurrentIngress.name: alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsCurrentIngress
alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsCurrentIngress.description: Count of Indexed packets ingress during current monitoring period.

alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsCurrentEgress.name: alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsCurrentEgress
alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsCurrentEgress.description: Count of Indexed packets egress during current monitoring period.

alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsLastIngress.name: alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsLastIngress
alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsLastIngress.description: Count of Indexed packets ingress during last monitoring period.

alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsLastEgress.name: alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsLastEgress
alaNetSecPortAnomalyStatsLastEgress.description: Count of Indexed packets egress during last monitoring period.

alaNetSecPortAnomalySummaryEntry.name: alaNetSecPortAnomalySummaryEntry
alaNetSecPortAnomalySummaryEntry.description: Summary are reported on a <port,summary-type,anomaly-type> basis

alaNetSecPortAnomalySummaryObserved.name: alaNetSecPortAnomalySummaryObserved
alaNetSecPortAnomalySummaryObserved.description: Count of observations for indexed anomaly on indexed port since monitoring was enabled.

alaNetSecPortAnomalySummaryDetected.name: alaNetSecPortAnomalySummaryDetected
alaNetSecPortAnomalySummaryDetected.description: Count of detections for indexed anomaly on indexed port since monitoring was enabled.

alaNetSecPortOpTable.name: alaNetSecPortOpTable
alaNetSecPortOpTable.description: Table for reporting port anomaly operation parameters

alaNetSecPortOpEntry.name: alaNetSecPortOpEntry
alaNetSecPortOpEntry.description: Each entry is identified by a unique port, and anomaly-type combination

alaNetSecPortOpCount.name: alaNetSecPortOpCount
alaNetSecPortOpCount.description: activation-count being used by netsec on the indexed object

alaNetSecPortOpSensitivity.name: alaNetSecPortOpSensitivity
alaNetSecPortOpSensitivity.description: sensitivity being used by netsec on the indexed object

alaNetSecPortOpPeriod.name: alaNetSecPortOpPeriod
alaNetSecPortOpPeriod.description: monitoring period being used by netsec on the indexed object

alaNetSecGroupOpTable.name: alaNetSecGroupOpTable
alaNetSecGroupOpTable.description: Table for reporting group anomaly operation parameters

alaNetSecGroupOpEntry.name: alaNetSecGroupOpEntry
alaNetSecGroupOpEntry.description: Each entry is identified by a unique group, and anomaly-type combination

alaNetSecGroupOpCount.name: alaNetSecGroupOpCount
alaNetSecGroupOpCount.description: activation-count being used by netsec on the indexed object

alaNetSecGroupOpSensitivity.name: alaNetSecGroupOpSensitivity
alaNetSecGroupOpSensitivity.description: sensitivity being used by netsec on the indexed object

alaNetSecGroupOpPeriod.name: alaNetSecGroupOpPeriod
alaNetSecGroupOpPeriod.description: monitoring period being used by netsec on the indexed object

alaNetSecGroupEntry.name: alaNetSecGroupEntry
alaNetSecGroupEntry.description: Each entry identifies a configured group

alaNetSecGroupMemberPorts.name: alaNetSecGroupMemberPorts
alaNetSecGroupMemberPorts.description: Yes if there are ports in this group.

alaNetSecGroupAnomalyCfg.name: alaNetSecGroupAnomalyCfg
alaNetSecGroupAnomalyCfg.description: Yes if any of this group's anomaly has a non-default configuration.

alaNetSecPortTrapAnomaly.name: alaNetSecPortTrapAnomaly
alaNetSecPortTrapAnomaly.description: Trap for an anomaly detected on a port.

alaNetSecPortTrapQuarantine.name: alaNetSecPortTrapQuarantine
alaNetSecPortTrapQuarantine.description: Trap for an anomalous port quarantine.

alaNetSecPortTrapInfoIfId.name: alaNetSecPortTrapInfoIfId
alaNetSecPortTrapInfoIfId.description: Interface index of port on which anomaly is detected

alaNetSecPortTrapInfoAnomaly.name: alaNetSecPortTrapInfoAnomaly
alaNetSecPortTrapInfoAnomaly.description: Type of anomaly detected on the interface

alaNetSecPortTrapInfoType.name: alaNetSecPortTrapInfoType
alaNetSecPortTrapInfoType.description: Nature of anomaly. Informs if system attached to interface is source or target of the anomaly.

alcatelIND1NETSECMIBConformance.name: alcatelIND1NETSECMIBConformance
alcatelIND1NETSECMIBConformance.description: Branch for NETSEC application conformance information

alcatelIND1NETSECMIBGroups.name: alcatelIND1NETSECMIBGroups
alcatelIND1NETSECMIBGroups.description: Branch for NETSEC application units of conformance

alcatelIND1NETSECMIBCompliances.name: alcatelIND1NETSECMIBCompliances
alcatelIND1NETSECMIBCompliances.description: Branch for NETSEC application compliance statements

alaNetSecPortRangeComplianceGroup.name: alaNetSecPortRangeComplianceGroup
alaNetSecPortRangeComplianceGroup.description: Collection of objects for management at port range level

alaNetSecMonitoringGroupComplianceGroup.name: alaNetSecMonitoringGroupComplianceGroup
alaNetSecMonitoringGroupComplianceGroup.description: Collection of objects for management at port group level

alaNetSecMonitoringGroupEntryGroup.name: alaNetSecMonitoringGroupEntryGroup
alaNetSecMonitoringGroupEntryGroup.description: Entry identifies configuration of a monitoring-group's anomaly-type's parameter group.

alaNetSecPortRangeGroupEntryGroup.name: alaNetSecPortRangeGroupEntryGroup
alaNetSecPortRangeGroupEntryGroup.description: Entry is identified by a unique port-range group.

alaNetSecPortTrapAnomalyGroup.name: alaNetSecPortTrapAnomalyGroup
alaNetSecPortTrapAnomalyGroup.description: Trap for an anomaly detected on a port group.
